Class ArrayGrid<T>

java.lang.Object
io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.datastructure.AbstractGrid<T>
io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.datastructure.ArrayGrid<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of cell values
All Implemented Interfaces:
Grid<T>, Serializable, Iterable<Grid.Entry<T>>
public class ArrayGrid<T> extends AbstractGrid<T> implements Serializable
An implementation of Grid which internally stores the elements with an array.

    • equals

      public boolean equals(Object o)

      Compares the specified object with this grid for equality. Two grids are considered equal if both the following condition hold:

      • they have the same width and height
      • for each cell, the elements in the two grid are either null or equal
      Overrides:
      equals in class Object
      Parameters:
